          <condition><![CDATA[if (Strcmp(Translate(Config_Options, true, "CreateCPIdentifiers", "Bloomberg_Connections"), "YES")
		&& AllHaveValue(ID_SEDOL1, EXCH_CODE))
	if (Strcmp(Translate(Config_Options, true, "CreateListingForUnlistedMarket", "Bloomberg_DL_Global_Preferred"),
			"YES"))
		return "IssueIdentifier";
	else if (Strcmp(Translate(Config_Options, true, "CreateListingForUnlistedMarket", "Bloomberg_DL_Global_Preferred"),
			"NO"))
		if (!Strcmp(EXCH_CODE, "UNKNOWN") && !Strcmp(EXCH_CODE, "NOT LISTED"))
			return "IssueIdentifier";
		else
			return "";
	else if (!OneOf("NO",
			Translate(Config_Options, true, "CreateListingForUnlistedMarket", "Bloomberg_DL_Global_Preferred"), "YES"))
		return ThrowMapError(Strcat(
				Translate(Config_Options, true, "CreateListingForUnlistedMarket", "Bloomberg_DL_Global_Preferred"),
				Strcat("--",
						"Wrong value in Config_Option.xml against Bloomberg_DL_Global_Preferred for CreateListingForUnlistedMarket . It is other than permitted value YES and NO value used in Config_option.xml")),
				"");
	else
		return "";
else if (Strcmp(Translate(Config_Options, true, "CreateCPIdentifiers", "Bloomberg_Connections"), "NO"))
	return "";
else if (!StrContainsOneOf(Translate(Config_Options, true, "CreateCPIdentifiers", "Bloomberg_Connections"), "YES",

  <Expressions>
    <Expression enabled="true" ident="KeyStreaming">
      <expr><![CDATA[if (OneHasValue(ID_BB_UNIQUE))
	return ID_BB_UNIQUE;
else if (OneHasValue(ID_BB_GLOBAL))
	return ID_BB_GLOBAL;
else if (OneHasValue(ID_ISIN))
	return ID_ISIN;
else if (OneHasValue(ID_BB_PARENT_CO))
	return ID_BB_PARENT_CO;
else if (OneHasValue(ID_BB_COMPANY))
	return ID_BB_COMPANY;
else
	return "";]]></expr>
    </Expression>
    <Expression enabled="true" ident="RecordIdentifier">
      <expr><![CDATA[if (AllHaveValue(ID_BB_UNIQUE, EXCH_CODE, MARKET_SECTOR_DES))
	return Strcat(ID_BB_UNIQUE, Strcat(";", Strcat(EXCH_CODE,
			Strcat(";", Strcat(MARKET_SECTOR_DES, Strcat(";", Strcat(ERRORCODE, Strcat(";", "OUT"))))))));
else if (AllHaveValue(SECURITIES, EXCH_CODE, MARKET_SECTOR_DES))
	return Strcat(SECURITIES, Strcat(";", Strcat(EXCH_CODE,
			Strcat(";", Strcat(MARKET_SECTOR_DES, Strcat(";", Strcat(ERRORCODE, Strcat(";", "OUT"))))))));
else
	return Strcat(SECURITIES, Strcat(";", Strcat(ERRORCODE, Strcat(";", "OUT"))));]]></expr>
    </Expression>
    <Expression enabled="false" ident="GSDMFiltering">
